  "description": {
    "zh": "你擅长用步枪吗？真是个怪问题，你敢信一个雇佣兵说自己不会用枪，这太夸张了……\n好吧好吧，证明一下你的作战技能如何？学习如何操控突击步枪，训练你的瞄准并学会控制后坐力。证明你的能力，士兵，我相信你。",
    "en": "Are you good with assault rifles? What a question, a soldier that doesn't know how to use a weapon, how ridiculous...\nAnyway, how about you prove your combat skills? Learn how to handle assault rifles, train your aim and learn how to control your recoil. Prove your skills warrior, I count on you."
